Okay.

305
00:12:07,999 --> 00:12:08,879
Thank you, Sis.

306
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:11,519
Mom,

307
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:12,840
did you buy the performance outfit

308
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:13,440
I sent in the group?

309
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:16,639
I...

310
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:17,879
I'll buy it soon.

311
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:23,639
Teen idol style.

312
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:26,799
What?

313
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:29,840
Have you

314
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,720
finished your papers?

315
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:33,039
Bring them over for me to sign.

316
00:12:33,159 --> 00:12:34,159
It's not me asking for it;

317
00:12:34,159 --> 00:12:34,840
your teacher mentioned it

318
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,759
in the group chat.

319
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,360
Just a bit left.

320
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,399
Finish it quickly.

321
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,440
Why bother?

322
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,440
Coming back

323
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,399
to press her with homework.

324
00:12:45,759 --> 00:12:46,279
No need for that.

325
00:12:47,039 --> 00:12:48,360
Am I pressing?

326
00:12:48,639 --> 00:12:50,600
I'm encouraging, okay?

327
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:51,919
Ask any kid who got into Tsinghua

328
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:52,720
or Peking University,

329
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,120
weren't they all encouraged like this?

330
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:54,999
Right, Sis?

331
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,159
Yes, exactly.

332
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,799
If I hadn't pushed you,

333
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:59,519
would you have made it to grad school?

334
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,720
See?

335
00:13:02,639 --> 00:13:03,240
Come.

336
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:05,039
Come.

337
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,320
Have some grapes.

338
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:07,799
People say

339
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:08,919
eating grapes

340
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:10,440
makes children fair-skinned.

341
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,519
Our second baby

342
00:13:12,519 --> 00:13:13,600
is called Little Grape.

343
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,360
Little Grape?

344
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,440
Named by Yunjie.

345
00:13:17,560 --> 00:13:18,399
What a coincidence!

346
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:22,039
Little Grape, Little Watermelon.

347
00:13:22,039 --> 00:13:22,999
Nice, nice.

348
00:13:22,999 --> 00:13:24,399
I love this name.

349
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,560
So sweet.

350
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:29,919
Finished so quickly?

351
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,240
An invitation?

352
00:13:33,639 --> 00:13:34,320
Inviting whom?

353
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,399
Inviting you!

354
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,600
How about it, Ms. Xu Meng'an?

355
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,039
I sincerely invite

356
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,440
You and Baby Little Grape

357
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:49,039
to attend my performance.

358
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,799
To experience a spiritual cleansing,

359
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,159
and also to give Little Grape

360
00:13:52,159 --> 00:13:53,440
a prenatal music lesson.

361
00:13:54,159 --> 00:13:55,560
You even know about prenatal education?

362
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:56,960
Of course!

363
00:13:56,999 --> 00:13:57,919
You told me before,

364
00:13:57,919 --> 00:13:58,799
when I was in your belly,

365
00:13:58,799 --> 00:14:00,039
I even listened to classical music.

366
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,159
You said listening to classical music

367
00:14:01,159 --> 00:14:02,399
would make me smart.

368
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,279
I didn't say that,

369
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:05,399
science says so.

370
00:14:06,159 --> 00:14:07,360
So leave Little Grape's prenatal education

371
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,720
to me!

372
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,759
Hey, Yunjie,

373
00:14:11,999 --> 00:14:12,480
what about me?

374
00:14:12,639 --> 00:14:14,080
Why isn't my name on it?

375
00:14:14,879 --> 00:14:15,960
We're so close,

376
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:16,840
we don't need formalities.

377
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:21,720
Doesn't matter,

378
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,639
I'll go whether I'm invited or not.

379
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:30,840
Your dad is feeling awkward,

380
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,039
Favoring me over him.

381
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:32,999
Not encouraged!

382
00:14:33,399 --> 00:14:34,560
I... I'll go comfort him.

383
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:43,080
You two guys,

384
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:44,480
over a meal of fried chicken,

385
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:45,639
is it really worth it?

386
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:28,240
Feeling jealous?

387
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:31,320
Do you feel like

388
00:15:31,320 --> 00:15:32,639
after raising her so painstakingly,

389
00:15:32,639 --> 00:15:34,519
I ended up picking the fruit?

390
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,360
It's okay, dear.

391
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,519
She'll surely take care of you in old age.

392
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:42,919
Of course, that goes without saying.

393
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,360
She just sees that you're

394
00:15:46,519 --> 00:15:47,200
pregnant,

395
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,320
and have been quite tired lately.

396
00:15:49,919 --> 00:15:51,879
So she wrote this to cheer you up.

397
00:15:51,919 --> 00:15:52,919
Why would I be jealous?

398
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:54,480
If that so,

399
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:55,799
I'd be quite pleased.

400
00:15:57,399 --> 00:15:58,399
But don't deny

401
00:15:58,399 --> 00:15:59,799
that you're feeling a bit jealous.

402
00:15:59,999 --> 00:16:00,720
To be honest,

403
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,320
are you feeling

404
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:03,440
a little sour inside?

405
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:05,840
Just a little,

406
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:07,159
a tiny bit.

407
00:16:11,639 --> 00:16:12,960
I knew it!

408
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,039
It says here,

409
00:16:16,039 --> 00:16:17,480
4:30 p.m. on Sunday afternoon.

410
00:16:18,159 --> 00:16:18,639
Yeah.

411
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:20,120
I thought it was in the morning,

412
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:22,039
like when she used to practice the piano.

413
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:23,919
What's wrong?

414
00:16:23,919 --> 00:16:25,600
They notified me today

415
00:16:25,799 --> 00:16:26,960
That I need to attend

416
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,560
an awards ceremony on Sunday afternoon.

417
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:30,159
They said I've been nominated.

418
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:32,360
Doesn't that clash with the recital?

419
00:16:32,639 --> 00:16:33,519
What should we do?

420
00:16:47,159 --> 00:16:47,720
Alright.

421
00:16:47,919 --> 00:16:49,320
I'll head out right away.

422
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,320
Little fairy!

423
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:53,879
Sis,

424
00:16:53,999 --> 00:16:55,159
look at our Yunjie,

425
00:16:56,639 --> 00:16:57,919
doesn't she look graceful?

426
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:59,039
Come, turn around.

427
00:17:00,799 --> 00:17:01,440
Beautiful.

428
00:17:01,999 --> 00:17:02,799
Stop!

429
00:17:04,679 --> 00:17:05,759
Two issues here.

430
00:17:06,679 --> 00:17:08,159
First, it's a bit plain.

431
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:08,960
Second,

432
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:10,759
wouldn't it be better

433
00:17:12,360 --> 00:17:14,120
to wear a vest over it?

434
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:16,239
Aunt, are you serious?

435
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:18,239
It's a bit revealing, dear.

436
00:17:21,959 --> 00:17:23,919
I think your aunt's suggestion

437
00:17:24,120 --> 00:17:25,040
is worth considering.

438
00:17:27,840 --> 00:17:29,439
How do you think I look in this outfit?

439
00:17:29,439 --> 00:17:30,479
It looks great!

440
00:17:30,719 --> 00:17:31,479
I think our girl

441
00:17:31,479 --> 00:17:33,239
can dress up a bit more.

442
00:17:34,120 --> 00:17:34,840
Yes, exactly!

443
00:17:38,439 --> 00:17:38,959
Li Lin,

444
00:17:40,239 --> 00:17:42,040
why are you dressed so sharp?

445
00:17:42,239 --> 00:17:43,280
I have to go too.

446
00:17:43,760 --> 00:17:44,280
Sis,

447
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:46,719
you mean well and always speak the truth,

448
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:47,959
but speaking the truth

449
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,800
should depend on the occasion, right?

450
00:17:50,320 --> 00:17:51,959
I do know the occasion!

451
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,280
Aren't we at home now?

452
00:17:53,439 --> 00:17:54,840
So, I have to speak the truth.

453
00:17:55,320 --> 00:17:56,719
Do you want me to lie instead?

454
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,239
Sometimes a little white lie

455
00:17:59,520 --> 00:18:00,360
is acceptable,

456
00:18:00,560 --> 00:18:01,600
to lighten the mood!

457
00:18:06,199 --> 00:18:07,360
I can't win an argument with you.

458
00:18:12,959 --> 00:18:14,399
Mom, you have so many

459
00:18:14,399 --> 00:18:15,679
girlish accessories!

460
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:17,280
I've never seen you wear them!

461
00:18:18,159 --> 00:18:19,120
Why does this one

462
00:18:19,120 --> 00:18:20,080
still have the tag on it?

463
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,280
It's new, of course.

464
00:18:22,439 --> 00:18:23,520
I like this kind of

465
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,600
bling-bling stuff too.

466
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:25,800
But there's just

467
00:18:26,239 --> 00:18:27,399
no chance to wear them.

468
00:18:27,959 --> 00:18:28,919
Then why did you buy them?

469
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:29,879
Such a waste of money.

470
00:18:30,000 --> 00:18:30,959
You always lecture me!

471
00:18:32,159 --> 00:18:33,080
Just bought them first.

472
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,520
They're all for you.

473
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:36,679
Then why don't you give them to me?

474
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:37,959
Apart from a few hair ties,

475
00:18:37,959 --> 00:18:38,959
what else have you given me?

476
00:18:39,239 --> 00:18:40,360
Any other good stuff?

477
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:41,159
Hand them over!

478
00:18:42,159 --> 00:18:43,159
I'm saving them all for you.

479
00:18:43,479 --> 00:18:45,040
For when you go to college.

480
00:18:45,840 --> 00:18:47,080
I knew you'd say that!

481
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,520
By the time I'm in college,

482
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:49,879
these will all be outdated.

483
00:18:49,879 --> 00:18:51,120
No way!

484
00:18:52,159 --> 00:18:53,199
This necklace looks nice.

485
00:18:53,199 --> 00:18:54,000
Try it on.

486
00:18:58,280 --> 00:18:58,800
How is it?

487
00:19:00,040 --> 00:19:00,560
Looks good!

488
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:01,639
Nice.

489
00:19:05,080 --> 00:19:06,560
But it's missing something.

490
00:19:09,239 --> 00:19:10,479
Here, this one.

491
00:19:15,760 --> 00:19:17,919
Looks great. See for yourself!

492
00:19:18,159 --> 00:19:19,120
Don't you look like a little princess?

493
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:21,399
So pretty!

494
00:19:21,959 --> 00:19:22,760
Looks nice, right?

495
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:23,959
Alright, let's go.

496
00:19:23,959 --> 00:19:25,000
My little princess!

497
00:19:26,719 --> 00:19:27,360
Meng'an,

498
00:19:28,159 --> 00:19:29,399
I got a scarf.

499
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,639
Put it on her.

500
00:19:30,639 --> 00:19:32,239
Look, the color is perfect!

501
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:34,560
Alright.

502
00:19:35,560 --> 00:19:36,600
Otherwise, it's too plain.

503
00:19:36,840 --> 00:19:38,800
See, how bright it is!

504
00:19:38,800 --> 00:19:39,159
Right!

505
00:19:39,159 --> 00:19:40,919
Little girls should wear bright colors.

506
00:19:41,639 --> 00:19:42,439
Exactly.

507
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:45,439
Mom, are you dressing me for winter?

508
00:19:46,280 --> 00:19:47,239
Thank your Aunt.

509
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:49,360
Thank you, Aunt.

510
00:19:50,239 --> 00:19:51,000
The back...

511
00:19:51,239 --> 00:19:52,239
It's covered.

512
00:19:53,639 --> 00:19:55,600
Now, with all this air conditioning,

513
00:19:55,760 --> 00:19:57,439
you must keep your chest and back warm.

514
00:19:57,439 --> 00:19:58,239
Got it?

515
00:19:58,679 --> 00:19:59,719
You're right.

516
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,520
We're out of time; we need to go.

517
00:20:03,159 --> 00:20:04,560
Alright, you go ahead.

518
00:20:04,560 --> 00:20:05,280
Bye, Aunt.

519
00:20:05,520 --> 00:20:06,639
Okay, bye-bye.

520
00:20:10,439 --> 00:20:11,840
None of you are easy.

521
00:20:12,760 --> 00:20:14,479
I really can't stand this.

522
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,320
And you're still siding with Aunt!

523
00:20:17,399 --> 00:20:18,280
From a health perspective,

524
00:20:18,280 --> 00:20:19,439
your aunt is right.

525
00:20:19,439 --> 00:20:21,320
Aesthetically, maybe not so much.

526
00:20:21,399 --> 00:20:22,600
Just go along with her a bit.

527
00:20:22,600 --> 00:20:23,560
What's the harm?

528
00:20:25,159 --> 00:20:25,639
Mom,

529
00:20:26,239 --> 00:20:27,239
you really are two-faced.

530
00:20:27,239 --> 00:20:28,080
First place!

531
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,280
Ladies,

532
00:20:30,679 --> 00:20:31,879
the car has been checked.

533
00:20:32,120 --> 00:20:32,919
You may get in.

534
00:20:35,199 --> 00:20:35,639
Please.

535
00:20:35,919 --> 00:20:37,120
Dad, you look so handsome today!

536
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:38,600
Now even drivers

537
00:20:38,600 --> 00:20:39,719
are as handsome as you?

538
00:20:40,159 --> 00:20:41,000
Industry competition, you know.

539
00:20:42,679 --> 00:20:43,679
No PDA in front of me!

540
00:20:44,239 --> 00:20:45,320
We're married, okay?

541
00:20:48,199 --> 00:20:48,840
Let's go.

542
00:20:54,360 --> 00:20:55,159
Watch carefully.

543
00:20:55,919 --> 00:20:57,239
He is going to open the car door for me.

544
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:03,159
Here we go!

545
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:23,520
Driving feels great today.

546
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:26,239
Like I'm riding the waves!

547
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:27,959
Keep it steady, please!

548
00:21:29,719 --> 00:21:30,239
Mom,

549
00:21:30,479 --> 00:21:31,439
you're amazing!

550
00:21:31,439 --> 00:21:32,520
Top 10 in the city!

551
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:35,040
Maybe you'll even win first place today.

552
00:21:35,719 --> 00:21:37,639
No, I'm just a nominee.

553
00:21:37,639 --> 00:21:38,520
Let's not exaggerate,

554
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:39,000
okay?

555
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,560
Out of ten winners,

556
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:41,719
you're definitely one of them!

557
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:43,800
I'm so proud!

558
00:21:44,360 --> 00:21:45,320
Last night, I was even upset

559
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:46,120
because you couldn't come with me

560
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:47,320
to my performance.

561
00:21:47,439 --> 00:21:48,560
I take back what I said.

562
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:49,479
Bring back a big trophy!

563
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:52,120
I feel like I've already won!

564
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:53,760
Won my daughter's approval.

565
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:57,360
My mom is awesome.

566
00:22:00,560 --> 00:22:03,120
If I could make it to the city's top 10,

567
00:22:04,439 --> 00:22:04,800
no,

568
00:22:05,159 --> 00:22:06,959
even the top 100...

569
00:22:08,239 --> 00:22:09,639
Your mom would smile in her sleep!

570
00:22:09,879 --> 00:22:11,239
Your dad would faint from happiness.

571
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:13,760
I was just saying.

572
00:22:13,919 --> 00:22:14,760
Don't pressure me.

573
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:16,639
Yunjie,

574
00:22:16,639 --> 00:22:17,560
if you have an idea,

575
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:18,639
you have to act on it.

576
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,760
The reason your mom

577
00:22:19,760 --> 00:22:20,719
has her achievements today

578
00:22:21,159 --> 00:22:22,399
is entirely because of her

579
00:22:22,639 --> 00:22:23,360
strong execution.

580
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:26,560
How about letting me

581
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,520
take over your studies?

582
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:28,840
No need!

583
00:22:30,239 --> 00:22:32,159
Look at you two!

584
00:22:38,679 --> 00:22:40,199
Hello, Ms. Zhang, good morning.

585
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:41,560
Wanzhen,

586
00:22:41,560 --> 00:22:42,919
I've sent you the electronic draft

587
00:22:42,919 --> 00:22:44,320
of the supply contract.

588
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:45,800
I've made a few more revisions.

589
00:22:45,800 --> 00:22:46,600
There should be no

590
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:48,360
legal loopholes now.

591
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:50,719
You can now secure legal financial rights

592
00:22:50,719 --> 00:22:52,639
for you and your child.

593
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:54,159
I'm truly happy for you.

594
00:22:54,320 --> 00:22:54,919
Ms. Zhang,

595
00:22:56,040 --> 00:22:57,239
I've thought about it all night.

596
00:22:57,479 --> 00:22:58,280
I've decided

597
00:22:59,320 --> 00:23:00,239
to give up the money.

598
