00:32:48,919 --> 00:32:49,879
repayment issues.

894
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:51,280
Ask Mr. Qian

895
00:32:51,479 --> 00:32:52,479
if his money has been redeemed.

896
00:32:54,120 --> 00:32:55,399
Stop talking nonsense here.

897
00:32:55,719 --> 00:32:57,120
I'm sticking with the company!

898
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:59,080
Mr. Qian, you're a smart man.

899
00:32:59,320 --> 00:33:00,479
After seeing that report,

900
00:33:00,919 --> 00:33:02,600
you should know what's going on, right?

901
00:33:02,800 --> 00:33:03,919
When the company is about to collapse,

902
00:33:04,120 --> 00:33:05,560
the first to exit

903
00:33:05,679 --> 00:33:06,560
are those in the know

904
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:08,040
before the investment products default.

905
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:08,679
And those left holding the bag

906
00:33:08,679 --> 00:33:10,239
are these innocent people.

907
00:33:11,479 --> 00:33:11,919
Feifei,

908
00:33:12,199 --> 00:33:12,600
Mr. Wu,

909
00:33:12,879 --> 00:33:13,919
you know how much you have bought,

910
00:33:13,919 --> 00:33:14,719
don't you?

911
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:15,879
Wanzhen,

912
00:33:15,879 --> 00:33:17,239
what should we do now?

913
00:33:17,760 --> 00:33:19,199
We demand immediate redemption.

914
00:33:19,399 --> 00:33:20,120
Yes, yes.

915
00:33:20,120 --> 00:33:21,639
We won't be the scapegoats.

916
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:12,360
Thank you to Zhouzhou

917
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:14,080
for the wonderful performance.

918
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:15,479
Next, let's welcome

919
00:34:15,479 --> 00:34:16,400
Wang Yunxi

920
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:17,359
to perform

921
00:34:17,359 --> 00:34:18,279
Etude in B minor.

922
00:34:22,199 --> 00:34:23,040
Excuse me.

923
00:34:23,040 --> 00:34:23,960
Sorry.

924
00:34:26,000 --> 00:34:26,440
Dad,

925
00:34:26,839 --> 00:34:28,080
I changed my number six to NO. 8.

926
00:34:28,080 --> 00:34:29,359
Mom should be able to make it, right?

927
00:34:29,359 --> 00:34:30,120
You changed it?

928
00:34:31,359 --> 00:34:32,719
You're something!

929
00:34:33,239 --> 00:34:33,839
Alright.

930
00:34:35,639 --> 00:34:36,920
Mom went on stage to get an award!

931
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:41,679
Mom looks beautiful!

932
00:34:41,679 --> 00:34:42,560
So elegant!

933
00:34:43,799 --> 00:34:44,759
What number is it now?

934
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,279
No. 6 now.

935
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:47,279
It's currently NO. 6.

936
00:34:47,639 --> 00:34:48,440
You're NO. 8.

937
00:34:48,719 --> 00:34:49,799
Isn't it almost your turn?

938
00:34:49,799 --> 00:34:50,440
Yes.

939
00:34:51,199 --> 00:34:51,960
No,

940
00:34:52,319 --> 00:34:53,880
I have to call your mom

941
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,279
and tell her to come quickly.

942
00:34:55,759 --> 00:34:57,080
Go on, sit down properly.

943
00:34:57,080 --> 00:34:57,839
Sit down, sit down.

944
00:35:01,839 --> 00:35:02,679
Hello, honey,

945
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:04,759
I'm done here.

946
00:35:04,759 --> 00:35:06,040
I'll be there right after a quick stop.

947
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:06,960
Alright.

948
00:35:07,279 --> 00:35:07,719
Tell the driver

949
00:35:07,719 --> 00:35:08,799
to speed up

950
00:35:08,799 --> 00:35:09,679
safely.

951
00:35:11,839 --> 00:35:12,480
Mom,

952
00:35:12,839 --> 00:35:13,520
I just saw the photo of you

953
00:35:13,520 --> 00:35:15,000
receiving the award on stage.

954
00:35:15,120 --> 00:35:16,120
You're beautiful and powerful,

955
00:35:16,159 --> 00:35:17,199
better than a celebrity.

956
00:35:17,639 --> 00:35:18,400
Thanks, sweetheart.

957
00:35:18,639 --> 00:35:19,440
I'll be there soon.

958
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,400
Alright, I'm waiting for you.

959
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:23,480
You really know how to lay it on thick.

960
00:35:24,040 --> 00:35:25,520
I'm just telling the truth.

961
00:35:26,880 --> 00:35:27,799
Why are you out again?

962
00:35:28,159 --> 00:35:28,520
Go back inside.

963
00:35:28,759 --> 00:35:29,279
Hurry up.

964
00:35:32,359 --> 00:35:33,480
Did I say something wrong?

965
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,679
You really are my mentor.

966
00:35:35,679 --> 00:35:37,239
And you did discover me.

967
00:35:37,759 --> 00:35:39,359
Wait, are you out of your mind?

968
00:35:39,639 --> 00:35:40,799
Performing for an audience?

969
00:35:40,920 --> 00:35:42,000
Who are you trying to impress?

970
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:43,000
How am I acting?

971
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:44,920
Every word I said is true.

972
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,239
Even if you kick me out,

973
00:35:46,440 --> 00:35:48,000
I'll still be grateful you discovered me.

974
00:35:48,159 --> 00:35:49,400
Can we stop this act, please?

975
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:50,480
Once the contract ends,

976
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:51,679
you can just leave.

977
00:35:52,359 --> 00:35:53,639
You go your way,

978
00:35:53,639 --> 00:35:54,759
I'll go mine.

979
00:35:54,759 --> 00:35:55,600
We're not connected.

980
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,239
Aren't you embarrassed?

981
00:35:58,480 --> 00:35:59,679
As long as I'm not embarrassed,

982
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,040
the awkwardness is on others.

983
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:01,839
Fine.

984
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:03,359
You win.

985
00:36:37,719 --> 00:36:38,359
What's wrong?

986
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:39,560
Not feeling well?

987
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:45,440
It's nothing.

988
00:36:45,679 --> 00:36:46,799
Just feeling a bit nauseous.

989
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:49,199
I'm leaving now.

990
00:37:07,759 --> 00:37:08,880
Quite attentive, aren't you?

991
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:10,159
Still waiting here.

992
00:37:10,719 --> 00:37:12,159
Yeah, yeah, waiting for what?

993
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:14,040
Your prized find.

994
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:16,600
Why wait for her? I'm waiting for you.

995
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:18,159
I'm not your mentor.

996
00:37:18,159 --> 00:37:18,960
Why wait for me?

997
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:19,600
No, it's just...

998
00:37:19,600 --> 00:37:20,279
Where are you headed?

999
00:37:20,279 --> 00:37:21,719
I'll drive you.

1000
00:37:21,719 --> 00:37:22,239
No need.

1001
00:37:22,520 --> 00:37:23,400
I'm going to find my daughter.

1002
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:25,000
Come on, just get in my car.

1003
00:37:25,199 --> 00:37:26,000
Let's talk.

1004
00:37:26,199 --> 00:37:27,000
I don't want to talk.

1005
00:37:27,759 --> 00:37:28,880
I have some intel.

1006
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:31,600
Interested?

1007
00:37:33,759 --> 00:37:35,040
You're no fun.

1008
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:36,120
We've been friends

1009
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,239
for over 20 years,

1010
00:37:37,359 --> 00:37:38,560
and now

1011
00:37:38,560 --> 00:37:39,359
I need to use intel

1012
00:37:39,359 --> 00:37:40,359
to chat?

1013
00:37:40,560 --> 00:37:41,000
Are you coming or not?

1014
00:37:41,239 --> 00:37:42,560
Alright, alright, let's go.

1015
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:43,239
Get in my car.

1016
00:38:03,719 --> 00:38:05,000
What's that smell in your car?

1017
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:08,960
No smell at all.

1018
00:38:13,679 --> 00:38:14,880
Is it the car freshener?

1019
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,000
Hey,

1020
00:38:17,560 --> 00:38:18,839
who bought this air freshener?

1021
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:20,880
Miss Huang gave it to us.

1022
00:38:24,239 --> 00:38:24,679
Stop the car.

1023
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:25,639
It's nauseating.

1024
00:38:26,199 --> 00:38:26,639
I want to get out.

1025
00:38:26,719 --> 00:38:27,319
No, no, no.

1026
00:38:27,319 --> 00:38:28,359
What are you doing?

1027
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:29,560
Lv.

1028
00:38:29,960 --> 00:38:30,679
Yes, Mr. Yu?

1029
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:32,639
Well,

1030
00:38:32,639 --> 00:38:33,639
is that a trash can up ahead?

1031
00:38:33,639 --> 00:38:34,759
Quick, throw that air freshener away.

1032
00:38:36,199 --> 00:38:37,040
Got it, Mr. Yu.

1033
00:38:48,759 --> 00:38:50,880
I had no idea who bought it.

1034
00:38:52,719 --> 00:38:53,560
It's disgusting.

1035
00:38:53,759 --> 00:38:54,480
Makes me want to vomit.

1036
00:38:55,799 --> 00:38:56,960
Such a big reaction.

1037
00:38:57,960 --> 00:38:58,600
Are you pregnant?

1038
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:08,679
Really pregnant?

1039
00:39:10,080 --> 00:39:10,799
Unbelievable.

1040
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:13,359
Wait, my Senior Li Lin

1041
00:39:13,359 --> 00:39:14,319
is really something.

1042
00:39:15,080 --> 00:39:17,359
Making you earn money outside,

1043
00:39:17,359 --> 00:39:18,799
and now having you bear a baby?

1044
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:19,839
Wanzhen

1045
00:39:19,839 --> 00:39:21,279
hasn't earning for you.

1046
00:39:21,279 --> 00:39:22,080
Where is he now?

1047
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:25,520
Hitting the sore spot, huh?

1048
00:39:25,520 --> 00:39:26,400
Can you chat properly?

1049
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,159
Nope.

1050
00:39:30,279 --> 00:39:30,560
Wait,

1051
00:39:30,560 --> 00:39:32,880
your career is quite stable now,

1052
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:34,279
on the rise.

1053
00:39:34,279 --> 00:39:35,679
Your position is solid.

1054
00:39:36,480 --> 00:39:38,000
Why have a baby now?

1055
00:39:38,319 --> 00:39:39,560
I'm having it because I'm pregnant.

1056
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:41,000
I talked to Mr. Zhang about it.

1057
00:39:42,560 --> 00:39:43,400
Anyway, now it's no longer

1058
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:44,239
a secret.

1059
00:39:46,560 --> 00:39:47,679
So,

1060
00:39:47,679 --> 00:39:49,080
this matter is all out in the open.

1061
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:51,880
I'm telling you,

1062
00:39:52,679 --> 00:39:54,000
I was just about to bring this up.

1063
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,600
Mr. Zhang is now scouting for people.

1064
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,239
Is he trying to replace you?

1065
00:39:58,120 --> 00:39:59,080
Gotten wind of it.

1066
00:40:00,839 --> 00:40:01,440
Lv,

1067
00:40:02,159 --> 00:40:03,560
put on your headphones.

1068
00:40:08,880 --> 00:40:10,080
Poor thing.

1069
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:12,040
Even the driver isn't yours?

1070
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:15,120
Better safe than sorry.

1071
00:40:17,719 --> 00:40:19,000
Mr. Zhang is recruiting,

1072
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:20,880
and he's reached Huang Sisi.

1073
00:40:21,279 --> 00:40:22,440
Is that supposed to be intel?

1074
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:23,319
I knew that long ago.

1075
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,759
But Huang Sisi can't make it.

1076
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,520
The salary and position she wants

1077
00:40:28,639 --> 00:40:29,400
are things Mr. Zhang can't offer.

1078
00:40:30,759 --> 00:40:32,880
That was the first negotiation.

1079
00:40:34,279 --> 00:40:34,960
If Huang Sisi

1080
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:36,120
knew you were pregnant,

1081
00:40:36,679 --> 00:40:37,799
she'd know that

1082
00:40:37,920 --> 00:40:38,839
you'd have a vacancy

1083
00:40:39,279 --> 00:40:40,400
in your position.

1084
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:41,040
When you're not in the company,

1085
00:40:41,120 --> 00:40:41,600
right?

1086
00:40:42,199 --> 00:40:43,319
If they negotiate again,

1087
00:40:43,719 --> 00:40:44,600
and each makes a compromise,

1088
00:40:45,040 --> 00:40:46,759
your position could

1089
00:40:46,759 --> 00:40:47,679
be in jeopardy.

1090
00:40:55,080 --> 00:40:55,719
Thank you.

1091
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:58,239
Let me tell you,

1092
00:41:02,080 --> 00:41:03,279
Huang Sisi,

1093
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:04,600
I know her very well.

1094
00:41:04,799 --> 00:41:06,759
She's very shrewd

1095
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:09,400
and loves taking shortcuts.

1096
00:41:09,400 --> 00:41:10,080
Be careful.

1097
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:15,000
Shortcuts are the longest route.

1098
00:41:15,159 --> 00:41:16,239
I'm not afraid.

1099
00:41:17,960 --> 00:41:18,679
Just be careful yourself.

1100
00:42:09,880 --> 00:42:10,679
Thanks to Youyou

1101
00:42:10,679 --> 00:42:12,319
for the wonderful performance.

1102
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,679
Next up, please enjoy

1103
00:42:13,679 --> 00:42:15,719
the sonata performed by Qin Xiyi,

1104
00:42:15,719 --> 00:42:17,920
the first movement of G Major Sonata.

1105
00:42:18,679 --> 00:42:20,040
I've switched to No. 12.

1106
00:42:23,679 --> 00:42:24,880
How much longer do you need?

1107
00:42:25,279 --> 00:42:26,480
I'm stuck in traffic!

1108
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,120
Hurry up, speed it up.

1109
00:42:30,679 --> 00:42:32,080
Your daughter is about to go on stage.

1110
00:42:32,239 --> 00:42:34,000
I'll definitely be there.

1111
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,600
There's traffic on the road.

1112
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:36,719
Just wait a bit.

1113
00:42:37,679 --> 00:42:38,600
It looks like your mom

1114
00:42:38,600 --> 00:42:39,960
is really stuck in traffic.

1115
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:40,920
Maybe just forget it.

1116
00:42:40,920 --> 00:42:41,639
Don't let her come.

1117
00:42:41,839 --> 00:42:42,520
No way!

1118
00:42:42,759 --> 00:42:43,520
It was my mom

1119
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,239
who made me learn the piano.

1120
00:42:44,239 --> 00:42:45,480
Today is the last lesson.

1121
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:47,759
Mom, I hope you can make it.

1122
00:42:48,319 --> 00:42:48,799
Yes.

1123
00:42:49,159 --> 00:42:51,040
Sweetie, mom will definitely be there.

1124
00:42:51,279 --> 00:42:51,920
Well,

1125
00:42:52,120 --> 00:42:53,880
maybe you could tell the teacher

1126
00:42:54,040 --> 00:42:55,880
to move a few acts behind?

1127
00:42:56,359 --> 00:42:57,679
I'm already the last.

1128
00:42:58,359 --> 00:42:59,560
How can that be the last?

1129
00:42:59,639 --> 00:43:00,560
That's called the finale.

1130
00:43:00,839 --> 00:43:02,080
You're so well-prepared,

1131
00:43:02,080 --> 00:43:02,759
you must be the finale.

1132
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:07,480
Ms. Xu Meng'an,

1133
00:43:08,000 --> 00:43:08,880
if you don't come,

1134
00:43:09,319 --> 00:43:10,600
don't regret it.

1135
00:43:11,199 --> 00:43:11,920
Wait.

1136
00:43:14,560 --> 00:43:16,080
Your mom said she'd be here for sure.

1137
00:43:16,359 --> 00:43:16,960
Don't worry.

